<plot>Pal, a young artist, falls in love with the prettiest girl in his art class, Iris. If there were one place he could wish to live, it would be on the edge of her eyelids, where she would have to notice him. After figuring out that he is too small to be seen, Pal realizes that the only thing he can control is painting Iris' dreams on the inside of her eyelids.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?186611</url></doc>
